<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>The concept reads as familiar. I believe there is an SCP article similar to this concept (my apologies for not remembering the specifics. I believe it was localised to censoring itself though). You can refer to it as a phenomena or object, as an entity it would still be a phenomena.</p>
