<p>This feels very reminiscent of stuff like <a href="/scp-5242">SCP-5242</a> or <a href="/scp-2565">Allison Eckhart</a> and I'm sure there's something that plays with the core a lot more closely than either of those; and so I'm left feeling very much like this needs to do a touch more with the idea.</p>
