<p>I guess at the end of the day, my core question is really: so what are you doing with this? There's like a lot of like, vague hypothesises mentioned in this and they all sound vaguely interesting but I don't really have an idea of how this is all going to come together to form a cohesive article that actually like, tells a story, y'know?</p>

