<p>So if i understood right, you wanted to know how all of these ideas will emerge and if they are gonna create a succesful story about all this or not.</p>
<p>So to be more specific about your questions, as i said before, there will be some clues all over the article some of these are like;</p>
<p>-Like why this scp doesnt somehow effect commitee, and why they are refusing to share any information else then not being related to said scp.</p>
<p>-Or another one like why an update after the description says that; now all personal that reads the file needs to take amnestics unless they are ongoing research personal about the said scp while this proposal made by an newly promoted comittee member whos name is blackboxed due to it</p>
<p>-Why the last of the theories about said scp was removed by ethics committee due to possible cognitohazard? Since when ethics comittee are dealing with that?</p>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
